Because they're always smiling.

1052
01:55:00,784 --> 01:55:04,079
Turtles don't smile.
They do. - They don't.

1053
01:55:05,205 --> 01:55:09,292
I don't think turtles smile.
They do, and they live forever.

1054
01:55:09,751 --> 01:55:14,297
