I'd pull the TV into the tub.

1059
01:55:33,898 --> 01:55:35,733
I hate that film!

1060
01:55:36,817 --> 01:55:39,278
I'd like to die as a little girl.

1061
01:55:39,695 --> 01:55:44,032
