Grace!

1135
02:04:49,156 --> 02:04:50,657
Go home!

1136
02:04:53,159 --> 02:04:55,787
Grace! No! Grace!

1137
02:05:37,825 --> 02:05:39,452
You promised!

1138
02:06:48,348 --> 02:06:51,643
For the last time, I heard a voice
that wasn't my mother's,

1139
02:06:52,102 --> 02:06:54,479
whispering, "Good morning, Columbus."

1140
02:06:54,937 --> 02:07:00,443
It didn't bother me. Then the voice
became lower and turned into a wind

1141
02:07:00,901 --> 02:07:04,988
